(42, 16, 2, 54, 5, 24, 24, 'give an account of thy stewardship', 'Judgment and Accountability Theme', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability in both passages. Luke 16:2 speaks of giving an account of stewardship, while 1 Timothy 5:24 discusses how some sins go before to judgment, indicating a process of evaluation.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 16, 2, 60, 4, 5, 5, 'give an account', 'Accountability in Stewardship and Judgment', 'This connection highlights the theme of accountability before authority. Both passages emphasize the necessity of giving an account, whether in stewardship or before judgment.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
